de.bpmnaftool.model.aristaflow.data
Interface DataElement

All Known Implementing Classes:
DataElementImpl
public interface DataElement

A DataElement holds one data attribute of any type, e.g. String or boolean. For read and write access from nodes, DataEdges need to be created.

Author:
Felix Härer
